data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER - BRING US YOUR OFFERS TODAY! You are not going to want to miss out on a chance to own this magnificent home. Surrounded by serene woods and beautiful landscapes is this newly renovated, private custom built 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath Cape Cod. The moment you drive up to the house, you can start enjoying the privacy and beauty that surrounds you. A Welcoming warm covered front porch invites you in to the front door to the main floor which boasts an open concept family room, foyer, and formal dining space with marvelous views. The eat-in kitchen has been fully renovated and has new stainless appliances. The large remodeled Primary Suite, along with additional updated 1/2 bath and laundry complete the MAIN level of this home. NEW roof, new HVAC, & more! JUST REDUCED
